          <h2>Seim Effects</h2>
          <p>I don't have a lot to say about Seim's presets at the moment except that I like them, but Silver 5 was released earlier this year, and I completely missed it. My oversight has now been remedied.</p>
          <p>For this recent image of the "Tree of Life" in Olympic National Park, I ran some auto adjustments for exposure -- peak laziness -- and then applied the <cite>Razors A</cite> preset and <cite>Gav's Yellow 12</cite> mod. Color wasn't doing much for me on this image, so the black and white definitely works here, and I got to this look very quickly indeed!</p>
